Class Sub_Tch_Crs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vahe.entities.Sub_Tch_Crs

  • @Entity
public class Sub_Tch_Crs
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a Sub_Tch_Crs object with the given properties. represents a link table between Subject and Teacher and Course tables in the school_db relational database. mapped by Hibernate.
